snippet.textDisplay:
So, I totally agree you deserve the King Of Subnautica title. I have been watching the old, old, OLD, series from 2015 with my daughter and there are SO MANY things you suggest there that they ended up adding! Either to the main game or even to Below Zero! I'd say you should rewatch them sometime. :P I actually watched them way back then as well, and you're the reason I started playing at all, lol.
You suggested the boost (like the sea truck now has), a portable fabricator (like the sea truck module), lockers that hang on walls, plus the energy efficiency thing they put your name on, and a few other things we found. And we're only on episode 10, lol. The devs made an amazing game, but you essentially helped make Subnautica even more amazing with just your ideas. That is truly an awesome thing.
(Disclaimer: I'm a hardcore Markimoo fan, btw, but sometimes ya gotta spread the love and give credit where it's due)
